Original dither shader by Sam Bigos (MIT license):
https://github.com/samuelbigos/godot_dither_shader

Bayer matrix textures by tromero (MIT):
https://github.com/tromero/BayerMatrix

Blue noise from Moments in Graphics:
http://momentsingraphics.de/BlueNoise.html

Algorithms referenced from:
- Surma "Ditherpunk": https://surma.dev/things/ditherpunk/
- Lucas Pope TIGSource devlog: https://forums.tigsource.com/index.php?topic=40832.msg1363742
- Rune Skovbo Johansen "Dither3D": https://runevision.com/tech/dither3d/
- Bj√∂rn Ottosson "Oklab": https://bottosson.github.io/posts/oklab/
- Jorge Jimenez IGN: "Next Generation Post Processing in Call of Duty: Advanced Warfare" (2014)
